744
01:24:53.420 --> 01:24:54.420
But let me go

745
01:25:23.950 --> 01:25:24.950
I am sad.

746
01:25:28.890 --> 01:25:29.890
Why?

747
01:25:31.000 --> 01:25:39.000
Turkish subtitles; <font color="#ff0000">ufukbaba</font>

