01:26:01.400 --> 01:26:02.500
What are you doing here?

749
01:26:09.120 --> 01:26:10.120
This is Mary.

750
01:26:12.080 --> 01:26:13.500
He is our therapist.

751
01:26:15.560 --> 01:26:16.560
